## Semantic Syntax Errors

  |
1 | match x:
2 |     case {"x": 1, "x": 2}: ...
  |                   ^^^ Syntax Error: mapping pattern checks duplicate key `"x"`
3 |     case {b"x": 1, b"x": 2}: ...
4 |     case {0: 1, 0: 2}: ...
